### Cast or Update a Vote (Requires Authentication)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/stations/1/votes/me
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "type": "POSITIVE"
}

### Get User's Vote (Requires Authentication)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/stations/1/votes/me
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Remove User's Vote (Requires Authentication)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/stations/1/votes/me
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

